WEBVTT

00:11.803 --> 00:14.598
<i>Some people
are destined for greatness,</i>

00:14.932 --> 00:16.600
<i>born under a lucky star.</i>

00:17.059 --> 00:20.604
<i>But me, I was destined for disaster.</i>

00:21.104 --> 00:23.106
<i>That was the story of my life.</i>

00:23.190 --> 00:26.401
<i>Only I would get kidnapped
in the middle of a kidnapping.</i>

00:27.778 --> 00:30.489
<i>Last thing I remembered,
I was zapping Roxy,</i>

00:30.989 --> 00:32.658
<i>and then I blacked out.</i>

00:33.116 --> 00:34.618
<i>It had to be Christian.</i>

00:34.701 --> 00:36.328
<i>He abducted that girl in Brazil.</i>

00:36.745 --> 00:37.829
<i>Who else could it be?</i>

00:44.711 --> 00:46.004
Stella Rose?

00:46.380 --> 00:47.214
Roxy?

00:47.589 --> 00:48.590
<i>Hola.</i>

00:49.800 --> 00:52.010
- Why would you?
- What? Kidnap you?

00:52.427 --> 00:54.096
Why were you gonna kidnap Roxy?

00:56.014 --> 01:00.519
Because I was worried
she was gonna beat me at Regionals.

01:00.852 --> 01:03.188
If that's what this is about,
I'll drop out. I promise.

01:03.272 --> 01:06.567
Oh, you think I'm threatened by you?
Dream on.

01:06.650 --> 01:07.818
Then why?

01:07.901 --> 01:09.528
Bob Armstrong.

01:10.821 --> 01:12.239
He doesn't coach me anymore.

01:12.573 --> 01:13.782
He coaches her.

01:14.741 --> 01:17.160
