01:18.120 --> 01:19.580
Let me go. You'll get caught.

01:19.663 --> 01:22.332
You'll go to jail.
- No.You'll go to jail.

01:22.416 --> 01:25.502
You stole the truck,
you tried to abduct Roxy,

01:26.086 --> 01:27.170
and I've got the proof.

01:28.171 --> 01:31.091
I still can't believe you let her
do that to me. It hurt like a bitch.

01:31.174 --> 01:32.676
Well, I had to make it look authentic.

01:33.385 --> 01:34.219
Help!

01:34.845 --> 01:37.264
- Help! Help!
- Ah, I knew we should have gagged her.

01:37.347 --> 01:40.350
I've been kidnapped
by two crazy bitches. Help!

01:41.226 --> 01:42.936
Help! Ow! Ow!

01:45.480 --> 01:48.191
<i>I couldn't believe
that this was actually happening.</i>

01:48.275 --> 01:50.027
<i>That I might have a threesome</i>

01:50.110 --> 01:53.864
<i>with the two people I loved most
in the entire world.</i>

01:53.947 --> 01:57.618
<i>I had always been taught that you couldn't
have your cake and eat it too,</i>

01:57.701 --> 01:59.411
<i>but maybe that was wrong.</i>

01:59.494 --> 02:02.581
<i>Maybe this was my chance
to be fully happy.</i>

