04:27.601 --> 04:30.479
No. Let's... we can't lose the momentum.
Come on.

04:30.562 --> 04:33.690
I know, Bob, but I have
an early appointment tomorrow.

04:33.774 --> 04:35.901
And we gotta get up early in the morning

04:35.984 --> 04:37.903
