04:41.948 --> 04:43.700
this is goodnight?

04:45.744 --> 04:48.038
<i>I couldn't let this
slip through my fingers.</i>

04:51.124 --> 04:52.918
- You coming?
- I don't know.

04:53.376 --> 04:57.631
I mean, if we're not getting divorced
and we're not breaking up,

04:58.673 --> 04:59.674
