12:03.056 --> 12:05.683
Dad. Put out a BOLO on the Weenmobile.

12:10.480 --> 12:13.483
<i>I had to recapture
the magic of the night before.</i>

12:13.942 --> 12:16.903
<i>If I could have them both,
I wouldn't have to choose,</i>

12:16.986 --> 12:20.156
<i>and that was the only way
I could truly be happy.</i>

12:28.122 --> 12:29.374
